## Linking to Features

When a roadmap item becomes a feature:

1. Create feature with `/feature <description>`
2. Update the roadmap item status to "Defined"
3. Add feature reference: `→ Feature 001`

Example:
```
| 001 | User Auth | Login/logout flow | Defined → Feature 001 |
```

