## Updating This Roadmap

Use `/roadmap` to update this document with new ideas, reorganize phases, or capture brain dumps.

The command will:
- Parse unstructured input into structured items
- Assign sequential IDs (001, 002, 003...)
- Suggest phase assignments
- Update status as items progress
